<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1078818" n="1r"/>
<opener><salute>Viro <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rendition="#sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimo</expan></choice> et toto Orbe Celeberrimo
         <lb/>Johanni <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/>Petrus Antonius <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelotti</rs></salute></opener>
<p>Ex <rs key="B_1715-11-16_991170515018105501" type="letter">nuperrimis tuis litteris</rs><note type="editorial">Johann I Bernoulli an Pietro Antonio Michelotti, 16. November 1715</note> a. d. XVI <choice><abbr>Calend.</abbr><expan>Calendarum</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Decem<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>br.</abbr><expan>Decembris</expan></choice> datis intellexi ad Vos pervenisse <rs key="brieftag" type="letter">binas meas
                <lb/>epistolas</rs><note type="editorial">Pietro Antonio Michelotti an Nikolaus I Bernoulli vom 8. August 1715 (000059201). Zweiten Brief nachweisen (?)</note> simul cum <rs key="biblio_6MW47K34" type="biblio">schedis</rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatianis</rs>.<note type="editorial">Nachweisen</note><!--EK: Prüfen ob Brief oder Riposta gemeint?--> Doctissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>mi Agnati Tui <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolai</rs> <rs key="B_1715-10-26_991170517051505501" type="letter">litteras</rs><note type="editorial">Nikolaus I Bernoulli an Pietro Antonio Michelotti, 26. Oktober 1715</note> cum ultima
             <lb/>responsione ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatum</rs><note type="editorial">Nachweisen</note> nondum accepi;
             <lb/>Statim ac ad me pervenerint, responsum vestr
             <lb/>italicam in linguam translatum Diario Veneto<!-- sachtag -->
<lb/>inseri summa diligentia curabo.</p>
<p>Gratias ago maximas pr iis qu scribere ad
         <lb/>me <unclear>v</unclear>oluisti ad dissipandos nonnullos errores qui<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>bus prpeditus mentem tuam non satis asse<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>qui poteram in <choice><abbr>eruditiss.<hi rendition="#sup">a</hi></abbr><expan>eruditissima</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Dissertat.</abbr><expan>Dissertatione</expan></choice> tua de motu
         <lb/>musculorum.</p>
<p>De Mathematum <rs type="organisation">Cathedra</rs> acquirenda non<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>dum desperatum est pro <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rendition="#sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimo</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnato</rs> Tuo:
             <lb/>etenim fieri potest ut a novo <rs type="organisation">Magistra<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<pb facs="1078819" n="1v"/>
<lb break="no"/>tu</rs> vocetur ad docendum uti ego quotidie
             <lb/>rogo pro bono <rs type="organisation">Archilycei Patavini</rs>.</p>
<p>Pro <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filio</rs> Tuo Doctissimo, quem ais intelli<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>gere omnia scripta Vestra, meque posse adiu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>vare in ipsis intelligendis, si patieris ut veniat
             <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetias</rs>, ipsum libenter tanquam meum Fili
             <lb/>suscipiam, eique Domi me cubiculum sine
             <lb/>expensis parabo, ac alimenta neccessaria
             <lb/>etiam sine sumptibus subministrabo
             <lb/>saltem si me adiuvare volet in
             <lb/>omnibus scriptis et inventis vestris intelli<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>gendis. Poteris igitur <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filium</rs> mittere quam<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>primum aut saltem ventura Quadragesima,
             <lb/>sciasque me ipsum magnopere fore ama<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>turum tanquam meum proprium filium. </p>
<p>Interim Te aut <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">filium</rs> tuum Doctissimum rogo
             <lb/>ut hanc equationem mihi resolvatis <formula>10000a-a^{3}</formula>
<lb/><formula>=3</formula>. Hc quatio resoluta dabit totam Tabellam
             <lb/>quam <rs key="pers_DE-588-118771167" type="person">Wallisius</rs> exhibuit in <choice><orig>oper.</orig><reg><abbr>Oper.</abbr><expan>Operum</expan></reg></choice> <choice><abbr>mathem.</abbr><expan>mathematicorum</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>volum.</abbr><expan>volumine</expan></choice>
<pb facs="1078820" n="2r"/>
<lb/>1<supplied>,</supplied> <choice><abbr>pag.</abbr><expan>pagina</expan></choice>  m 1059 pro inveniendis singulis subleva<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tionibus ponderis <formula>P</formula> ope vesic spiritu humano
             <lb/>inflat. Valorem ipsius a ex quatione data non<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>dum potui recte elicere. In casu quo ha<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>bemus <formula>10000a-a^{3}=3</formula> invenit <rs key="pers_DE-588-118771167" type="person">Wallisius</rs> <formula>a=</formula>
<lb/><formula>NP=09.999,849,999,66</formula>.<note type="editorial">Dokument online einsehbar auf https://archive.org/stream/bub_gb_ER3j2xwScxsC#page/n1109 siehe erste Zeile rechts</note> Peto ut modum inveniendi
             <lb/>hosce valores mihi indicetis.</p>
<p>Cupio ut me admoneas de Adventu <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rendition="#sup">i</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filii</rs>
<lb/>Tui ut neccessaria pro ipso parare possim.
         <lb/>Spero quod <choice><abbr>Doctiss.<hi rendition="#sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Doctissimus</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnatus</rs> Tuus miserit suas
         <lb/>litteras per <rs key="place_VER-tirola" type="place">Tyrolim</rs>; illa enim  via certa:
         <lb/>interim obstupesco quod ad me nondum pervenerint.</p>
<p>Ego sum paratissimus ad omnia mandata
         <lb/>vestra, salutem plurimam mitto Clarissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>mis Viris <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filio</rs> et Agnato Tuo <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao</rs>.</p> <closer><salute>Vale
            <lb/>et fave.</salute> <dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <date when="1715-12-05">Nonis Decembris
               <lb/>MDCCXV</date></dateline></closer>
<pb facs="1078821" n="2v"/>
